Instead of just using original image, convert image using filter.
Vertical Edge Detection (Tensorflow, tf.nn.conv2d)
e.g. (scalar product)
image                 filter               converted image
3 1 2 4 2             1 0 -1               7 -5 1
5 2 1 3 2      ->     1 0 -1               3 -3 -1
5 2 3 3 1             1 0 -1
0 1 3 2 5


